            <p>A from the ground up remake of the original Tomb Raider has been announced at The Game Awards.</p>
<p>As <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/major-tomb-raider-announcement-leaks-ahead-of-the-game-awards">leaked earlier today</a>, this remake is known as Tomb Raider: Legacy of Atlantis. It places players back in the shoes of Lara Croft as she hops from country to country in search of the Scion of Atlantis. </p>
<!-- code from Primis - Eurogamer.net - eurogamer.net -->
<div>
<p><span data-type="targeting">
