</span> </p>
</div>
<!-- code from Primis -->
<p>Unlike the original game and the remastered collection that was released last year, this version of the first Tomb Raider has a certain cinematic 'Uncharted-ness' to it.
</p>
<p>Lara, meanwhile, has had a bit of a makeover, with her character model in Legacy of Atlantis sporting the classic tank top and short shorts look, but with the jade necklace first introduced in 2013's Tomb Raider reboot. You can see how it all looks in the new Tomb Raider: Legacy of Atlantis trailer below.</p>

