            <p>Crystal Dynamics and Amazon's all new <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/tomb-raider-games-order">Tomb Raider game</a> has, after years of waiting, finally been revealed.</p>
<p>It is known as Tomb Raider: Catalyst, and as previously rumoured sees a more mature Lara Croft back on her globe-spanning adventures, this time popping over to India for a spot of tomb raiding.</p>
<p>A new trailer, which you can see below, shows Lara using her dual pistols, which makes me very happy.</p>

