<p>As for Tomb Raider more generally, in addition to today's game announcement, Amazon also has a live-action TV series in the works, <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/amazons-live-action-tomb-raider-series-has-found-its-lara-croft">with Sophie Turner set to play Lara</a>. Earlier this week, it was reported <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/amazon-eyes-alien-actress-sigourney-weaver-for-live-action-tomb-raider-series">Sigourney Weaver was also in talks to star in the show</a>, which is due to begin filming next month.</p>

